Who We Are and What This Policy Covers
No personal data is stored or saved. 

We won’t share your personal data with any third party which is not related with Unlaced.

Unlaced may amend this Privacy Statement from time to time. Use of information we collect now is subject to the Privacy Statement in effect at the time such information is used. If we make changes in the way we use personal information, we will notify you by posting an announcement on our Site or a notification through the Unlaced app. Users are bound by any changes to the Privacy Statement when he or she uses or otherwise accesses the Application after such changes have been first posted. 

If you have any questions or concerns on how this data is handled, contact us at unlaced [at] urbansory.com with a detail description of your concern.

Effective: May 1, 2013
Please note that this Privacy Policy does not apply to any of our products or services that have a separate privacy policy.
Privacy Policy Changes
Although most changes are likely to be minor, Unlaced may change its Privacy Policy from time to time. Unlaced encourages visitors to frequently check this page for any changes to its Privacy Policy. If we make changes, we will notify you by revising the change log below. Your further use of the Services after a change to our Privacy Policy will be subject to the updated policy.
